00:30:04,432 --> 00:30:06,619
How could this happen?

281
00:30:07,127 --> 00:30:08,619
I have no idea.

282
00:30:10,601 --> 00:30:12,779
Where’s Win?

283
00:30:15,811 --> 00:30:17,912
Here’s the thing.

284
00:30:17,912 --> 00:30:20,848
Not long after Win woke up in your body,

285
00:30:20,848 --> 00:30:22,819
