286
00:30:23,234 --> 00:30:26,549
and told Win to collect holy water from four monks within 7 days

287
00:30:26,549 --> 00:30:28,466
so he could perform a ritual.

288
00:30:30,109 --> 00:30:31,819
Is he traveling alone?

289
00:30:32,880 --> 00:30:34,505
He’s traveling with Korn.

290
00:30:34,505 --> 00:30:36,100
What?

291
00:30:36,223 --> 00:30:38,179
Win is with Korn?

292
00:30:38,660 --> 00:30:41,361
He wouldn't go with him at first,

293
00:30:41,361 --> 00:30:46,099
but the Venerable Uncle said they need each other to complete the mission.

294
00:30:48,632 --> 00:30:52,179
Anyway, there’s something you need to do as well.

295
00:30:55,674 --> 00:30:57,539
What is it?

296
00:31:01,020 --> 00:31:04,845
No one else knows you and Win have switched bodies,

297
00:31:04,845 --> 00:31:06,139
except me and Korn,

298
00:31:06,638 --> 00:31:10,139
so you must pose as Win

299
00:31:10,877 --> 00:31:12,659
until he comes back with the holy water.

300
00:31:25,777 --> 00:31:27,002
Win is safe now.

301
00:31:27,002 --> 00:31:29,106
Can I go see him?

302
00:31:29,410 --> 00:31:30,906
I don’t think that’s a good idea for now.

303
00:31:30,906 --> 00:31:32,327
He just woke up.

304
00:31:32,327 --> 00:31:34,739
Let me examine his overall conditions.

305
00:31:34,739 --> 00:31:38,005
If all is clear, I’ll have him moved to the IPD.

306
00:31:38,005 --> 00:31:39,717
After that, you guys can see him.

307
00:31:41,096 --> 00:31:42,739
I’m relieved.

308
00:31:42,850 --> 00:31:44,739
No more worrying.

309
00:31:45,357 --> 00:31:47,505
Thank you so much, Non.

310
00:31:47,500 --> 00:31:50,542
I told you nothing was going to happen to Win.

311
00:31:50,542 --> 00:31:52,619
That kid is tough.

312
00:31:54,362 --> 00:31:58,099
So that means the holy water thing is not real.

313
00:32:02,931 --> 00:32:04,840
What a waste of time.

314
00:32:09,071 --> 00:32:10,100
Korn.

315
00:32:10,100 --> 00:32:11,337
Yes?

316
00:32:11,874 --> 00:32:13,139
What time is it?

317
00:32:14,305 --> 00:32:15,539
Almost 4 p.m.

318
00:32:19,071 --> 00:32:21,539
Do you want to get up?

319
00:32:21,856 --> 00:32:23,539
Slowly.

320
00:32:37,136 --> 00:32:40,856
It takes many hours to get to my house from here.

321
00:32:43,368 --> 00:32:44,739
