325
00:33:19,715 --> 00:33:21,477
You can do it.

326
00:33:21,477 --> 00:33:23,205
Your mother is on her way.

327
00:33:25,168 --> 00:33:26,059
Win.

328
00:33:26,059 --> 00:33:28,059
My son.

329
00:33:30,979 --> 00:33:32,568
Mom.

330
00:33:38,444 --> 00:33:41,293
I already examined his overall conditions.

331
00:33:41,293 --> 00:33:44,379
