336
00:34:01,241 --> 00:34:02,979
I’m sorry.

337
00:34:09,665 --> 00:34:12,979
How are you feeling?

338
00:34:17,115 --> 00:34:18,979
I’m fine.

339
00:34:20,225 --> 00:34:22,979
I’m perfectly fine.

340
00:34:24,013 --> 00:34:26,536
I probably slept too much.

341
00:34:27,500 --> 00:34:29,499
Are you hurt anywhere?

342
00:34:31,109 --> 00:34:33,059
Not at all.

343
00:34:35,045 --> 00:34:39,059
