349
00:35:06,148 --> 00:35:07,499
Oh, yes.

350
00:35:08,112 --> 00:35:11,499
Lin is collecting the holy water to ward off your bad luck.

351
00:35:11,816 --> 00:35:15,287
She asked me to keep some bottles.

352
00:35:15,287 --> 00:35:17,659
I’ll go bring them here.

353
00:35:18,454 --> 00:35:19,457
That’s great.

354
00:35:19,457 --> 00:35:21,659
