374
00:36:36,414 --> 00:36:38,294
Are you saying I’m fat?

375
00:36:38,294 --> 00:36:40,859
No, I’m not saying you’re fat.

376
00:36:40,859 --> 00:36:42,234
You’re just big.

377
00:36:42,230 --> 00:36:43,579
You’re the worst.

378
00:36:43,579 --> 00:36:44,200
Watch it.

379
00:36:44,200 --> 00:36:46,859
