380
00:36:47,582 --> 00:36:48,859
Stop it.

381
00:36:50,496 --> 00:36:52,850
It’s the truth.

382
00:37:01,992 --> 00:37:03,601
Win.

383
00:37:06,090 --> 00:37:08,189
Are you mad at me?

384
00:37:08,189 --> 00:37:10,189
No.

385
00:37:10,790 --> 00:37:12,859
I’m just thinking

386
00:37:13,471 --> 00:37:18,314
