00:45:09,613 --> 00:45:12,979
How are things going?

468
00:45:28,665 --> 00:45:30,597
Win.

469
00:45:43,244 --> 00:45:45,290
Korn.

470
00:45:48,927 --> 00:45:50,339
You’re safe now, Lin.

471
00:46:04,414 --> 00:46:06,189
